00:21:45,872 --> 00:21:47,139
[ITAMI] The Piper?

455
00:21:47,239 --> 00:21:49,105
[GREY] Yes. He's one of the
assassins

456
00:21:49,205 --> 00:21:50,239
most recently hired.

457
00:21:50,339 --> 00:21:51,739
[GREY] He's extremely deadly,

458
00:21:51,839 --> 00:21:53,672
the two of us would be no match
for him.

459
00:21:53,772 --> 00:21:55,072
[RORY] Given her achievement

460
00:21:55,172 --> 00:21:57,405
of killing the flame dragon, it
is no surprise.

461
00:21:57,505 --> 00:22:00,772
[SHANDY] If you please,
we will need your assistance
with this, Itami.

462
00:22:00,872 --> 00:22:04,039
[ITAMI] No one needs to beg me.
I'll protect Lelei anyday.

463
00:22:04,139 --> 00:22:05,839
[GREY] You're the man in green
I've been hearing about.

464
00:22:05,939 --> 00:22:07,805
[GREY] Why don't the two of us
join forces

465
00:22:07,905 --> 00:22:09,772
and take out these cowardly
assassins.

466
00:22:09,872 --> 00:22:10,639
[ITAMI] I don't think so.

467
00:22:12,739 --> 00:22:14,339
[ITAMI] I've a better idea...

468
00:22:14,439 --> 00:22:15,439
Run away.

469
00:23:45,905 --> 00:23:48,339
[LELEI] Next time on Gate:

470
00:23:48,439 --> 00:23:50,072
The Lovers.

